{"tid":1817400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國會報告批評中國侵蝕香港自治　建議執行《人權法案》開始制裁","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:03:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"24a7921908a2ab470c9d9373c9e34ba469df9a62","tid":1817400,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1501791_2_L_20200109095519.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1501791_2_L_20200109095519.jpg&h=d1330953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501791-20200109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501791-20200109.htm&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF04ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=84be665c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501791-20200109.htm&h=bcbcb507\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501791-20200109.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國會一個委員會發表年度報告，認為中國在過去一年以來，進一步侵蝕香港的自由及自治權，有關做法影響美國未來的對港政策。<br />\n<br />\n報告建議華府執行《香港人權與民主法案》，懲罰違反人權的人士。<br />\n<br />\n報告由跨黨派的國會及行政當局中國委員會撰寫，提及特區政府雖然撤回修訂逃犯條例，但市民要求追究警方使用過度武力以及被指與黑社會聯手對付示威者。報告又提及多名民主派議員被禁止競選公職，以及多名參與爭取民主運動人士被囚禁。<br />\n<br />\n報告又談及新疆至少有過百萬名穆斯林被關押在教培中心，認為中國當局違反人權，建議對參與大規模監禁和監視維吾爾人的中國企業和官員實施制裁。"},{"pid":"c7af7438b85b0bfd74968295bc8deacfcda0134a","tid":1817400,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:13:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"18eaf8b627018845b8af9e8fe257ddef4a5dc5c6","tid":1817400,"uid":70147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=